# The scripts directory holds inspect / dev / one-off tooling the image
# doesn't need — exclude it to keep the build context small. The ONE exception
# is `scripts/migrate.ts`: the builder stage runs `npx esbuild scripts/migrate.ts`
# to bundle the migrate-Job entrypoint into `migrate.cjs`, so that single file
# must reach the build context (its `lib/` imports are not excluded). Keep the
# negation in lockstep with the Dockerfile's esbuild step.
scripts
!scripts/migrate.ts
